    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable ride that won't let you down? This good-condition vehicle is a fantastic choice for drivers who want dependable, everyday transportation without the premium price tag of a mint-condition car! It runs smoothly, handles daily commutes and weekend adventures with ease, and has been well cared for over its lifetime. While it may show some normal signs of use, it's mechanically sound and ready to serve its next owner faithfully. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Don't miss this great opportunity to own a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly, handles reliably, and features a clean, well-kept interior that you'll appreciate every day. The exterior presents nicely with only the minor wear you'd expect from a regularly driven car. If you're looking for a solid, trustworthy ride without paying mint-condition prices, this one deserves a closer look!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in good condition, and we want any potential buyer to have a clear, accurate picture before reaching out. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains a reasonable shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use. There are no major dents or rust concerns, though close inspection will reveal the small imperfections you'd expect from a vehicle that has been driven regularly. The interior is clean and functional, with seats showing modest wear but no tears or major staining. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 all primary systems are in good working order, and there are no known outstanding issues. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been maintained appropriately and is ready for everyday use. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a solid, reliable option for buyers looking for a well-maintained used car. The exterior shows only minor signs of normal wear \u2014 small scuffs or light scratches consistent with everyday use \u2014 but retains a presentable, clean appearance overall. The interior is in good shape with no major damage, though you may notice typical signs of use such as light wear on high-contact surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been properly maintained; it's ready for daily driving without any immediate repair concerns. This is an honest, straightforward listing for a dependable vehicle at a fair price \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
